				\begin{document}$$Foxp{2^{S321X/+}}$$\end{document}Foxp2S321X/+ mice and wild-type littermate controls were injected intraperitoneally with either vehicle (DMSO) or 0.1 mg/kg picrotoxin (Tocris, Bristol, UK). Injection was done by hand and mice were placed back in their home cage for 10 min following injection, after which mice were placed on the accelerating rotarod.

